{"ID":270260, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"260\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs259.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs261.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 260<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Baptism for the Dead<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">A few very important things have been manifested to me in my absence respecting the doctrine\n  of baptism for the dead, which I shall communicate to the Saints next Sabbath, if nothing should\n  occur to prevent me.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <p class=\"std\">President Smith said, &ldquo;I have one remark to make respecting the baptism for the dead<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> to suffice\n  for the time being, until I have opportunity to discuss the subject at greater length&mdash;all persons\n  baptized for the dead must have a recorder present,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> that he may be an eyewitness to record<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> and\n  testify of the truth<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> and validity of his record. It will be necessary, in the Grand Council, that these\n  things be testified to by competent witnesses. Therefore let the recording and witnessing of baptisms\n  for the dead be carefully attended to from this time forth. If there is any lack, it may be at the\n  expense of our friends; they may not come forth.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> (Aug. 31, 1842.) DHC 5:139-141.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Persecution the Heritage of the Righteous<\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic centerEmphasis\">From an Editorial in the &ldquo;Times and Seasons,&rdquo; by the Prophet<\/div>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <p class=\"std\">Abel was slain for his righteousness,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> and how many more up to the flood is not of much\n  consequence to us now. But if we believe in present revelation, as published in the &ldquo;Times and\n  Seasons&rdquo; last spring, Abraham, the prophet of the Lord, was laid upon the iron bedstead for\n  slaughter;<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> and the book of Jasher,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> which has not been disproved as a bad author, says he was cast\n  into the fire of the Chaldees. Moses, the man of God,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> who killed an Egyptian persecutor of the\n  children of Israel, was driven from his country and kindred.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> Elijah had to flee his country, for they\n  sought his life,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span>&mdash;and he was fed by ravens.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> Daniel was cast into a den of lions:<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> Micaiah was fed\n  on the bread of affliction;<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> and Jeremiah was cast into the filthy hole under the Temple;<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> and did\n  these afflictions come upon these prophets of the Lord on account of transgression? No!  It was the\n  iron hand of persecution<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>&mdash;like the chains of Missouri!  And mark&mdash;when these old prophets\n  suffered, the vengeance of God, in due time,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> followed and left the wicked opposers of the Lord&rsquo;s\n  anointed<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> like Sodom and Gomorrah;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> like the Egyptians;<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109597\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109597)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109597)\">1 Cor. 15:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115952\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115952)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115952)\">D&amp;C 124:28-36<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116091\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116091)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116091)\">D&amp;C 127:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116100\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116100)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116100)\">D&amp;C 128:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108392\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108392)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108392)\">Luke 1:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110523\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110523)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110523)\">2 Pet. 1:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111273\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111273)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111273)\">2 Ne. 27:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108682\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108682)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108682)\">John 5:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112283\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112283)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112283)\">Alma 40:21<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116142\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116142)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116142)\">D&amp;C 128:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116789\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116789)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116789)\">Moses 5:26,32<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116982\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116982)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116982)\">Abr. 1:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106365\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106365)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106365)\">Josh. 10:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106404\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106404)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106404)\">2 Sam. 1:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106350\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106350)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106350)\">Deut. 33:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106089\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106089)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106089)\">Ex. 2:11-15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109022\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109022)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109022)\">Acts 7:22-29<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106457\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106457)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106457)\">1 Kgs. 19:9-10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106450\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106450)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106450)\">1 Kgs. 17:1-7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107537\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107537)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107537)\">Dan. 6:1-28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106308\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106308)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106308)\">Deut. 16:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106464\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106464)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106464)\">1 Kgs. 22:26-28<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107131\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107131)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107131)\">Isa. 30:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107401\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107401)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107401)\">Jer. 32:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107411\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107411)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107411)\">Jer. 38:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110941\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110941)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110941)\">1 Ne. 7:14<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115899\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115899)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115899)\">D&amp;C 123:8-9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106345\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106345)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106345)\">Deut. 32:35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112809\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112809)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112809)\">Morm. 8:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113438\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113438)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113438)\">D&amp;C 24:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113822\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113822)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113822)\">D&amp;C 43:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114974\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114974)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114974)\">D&amp;C 90:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106395\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106395)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106395)\">1 Sam. 16:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106659\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106659)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106659)\">Ps. 20:6<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115750\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115750)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115750)\">D&amp;C 121:16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116550\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116550)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116550)\">D&amp;C 135:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106035\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106035)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106035)\">Gen. 19:24<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106113\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106113)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106113)\">Ex. 7:1-25<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106114\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106114)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106114)\">Ex. 8:1-32<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106115\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106115)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106115)\">Ex. 9:1-35<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106116\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106116)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106116)\">Ex. 10:1-29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106117\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106117)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106117)\">Ex. 11:1-10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106118\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106118)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106118)\">Ex. 12:1-51<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106119\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106119)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106119)\">Ex. 13:1-22<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106120\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106120)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106120)\">Ex. 14:1-31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}